Localization.Name: Tekaw Pants
Localization.Description: Carrying Capacity: 1K µSCU\n\nComfortable enough to wear all day yet designed to thrive under harsh conditions, the Tekaw pants are perfect whether you're on or off duty. Their stylish yet durable design includes a water-wicking coating and padded shins guards with wrappings that ensure a snug fit.
